WEBVTT

00:00.410 --> 00:05.230
Hey, Lain. Do you think that you’re a special person?

00:05.230 --> 00:06.520
Special?

00:06.520 --> 00:11.880
Everyone says, "Lain is not a normal girl" and "Isn’t she dangerous?"

00:11.880 --> 00:15.440
I’ve known you since we were children, so I say to them "No, she is normal."

00:15.770 --> 00:18.240
Also, I’m a little similar to you.

00:18.240 --> 00:21.800
It makes me sad that I’m not special like other people!

00:21.800 --> 00:26.250
Do you think so? I don’t care if I’m an ordinary person.
